MURDERED? THINK SHE LIKED PAIN?

11:12.770 --> 11:14.328
THINK SHE GOT A LITTLE DIZZY?

11:14.340 --> 11:15.739
>> I DIDNT KILL HER.

11:15.740 --> 11:16.695
>> [CHUCKLES] THATS NOT WHAT

11:16.700 --> 11:17.689
THE JURY THOUGHT. OR THE APPEALS

11:17.700 --> 11:18.860
COURT, OR THE GOVERNOR.

11:18.870 --> 11:21.407
>> THEY--THEYRE ALL WRONG.

11:21.410 --> 11:22.707
BECAUSE I DIDNT DO IT.

11:22.710 --> 11:23.677
>> OH, COME ON, WES. SHE

11:23.680 --> 11:24.749
COMPLAINED ABOUT YOU PEEPING IN

11:24.750 --> 11:25.739
HER WINDOWS. THEY FOUND YOUR

11:25.750 --> 11:27.399
BOOT PRINT IN HER APARTMENT,

11:27.410 --> 11:29.071
IN HER BLOOD.

11:29.080 --> 11:29.978
>> WELL, I SHOULDNT HAVE

11:29.990 --> 11:31.685
PEEPED. I SHOULDNT HAVE PEEPED,

11:31.690 --> 11:33.317
BUT I DIDNT KILL HER.

11:33.320 --> 11:34.355
OW!

11:34.360 --> 11:35.952
>> YOU KNOW WHAT, SLING BLADE,

11:35.960 --> 11:37.359
THAT OLD-TIMEY "I DIDNT DO

11:37.360 --> 11:38.679
NOTHIN" HICK SHIT JUST DONT

11:38.690 --> 11:39.861
WORK FOR ME.

11:39.870 --> 11:42.964
>> I CAME HOME AND HER DOOR WAS

11:42.970 --> 11:44.790
OPEN, AND I LOOKED INSIDE TO SEE

11:44.800 --> 11:47.689
IF...SHE WAS OK. SHE WAS

11:47.700 --> 11:49.361
A NICE GIRL.

11:49.370 --> 11:51.474
DID YOU KNOW DEAD BODIES,

11:51.480 --> 11:53.835
THEY DONT LOOK LIKE THEY DO

11:53.840 --> 11:58.732
ON--ON TV. THEY LOOK...RUBBERY.

11:58.740 --> 12:01.413
LIKE A PICTURE, YOU KNOW.

12:01.420 --> 12:03.445
NO SOUL.

12:03.450 --> 12:06.715
I GOT SCARED AND I RAN AWAY.

12:06.720 --> 12:08.938
I KNOW I SHOULD--

12:08.950 --> 12:10.759
I KNOW I SHOULDNT HAVE.

12:10.760 --> 12:11.795
I KNOW I SHOULD HAVE CALLED

12:11.800 --> 12:14.792
THE POLICE. I KNOW I MESSED UP.

12:14.800 --> 12:16.791
BUT I DIDNT KILL HER.

12:16.800 --> 12:17.994
>> TELL IT TO YOUR PRIEST.

12:18.000 --> 12:19.900
>> IVE BEEN TELLING EVERYONE.

12:19.910 --> 12:22.060
FOR 15 YEARS.

12:22.070 --> 12:24.800
NO ONES LISTENED.

12:24.810 --> 12:27.404
DOESNT MATTER ANYMORE.

12:27.410 --> 12:30.345
DONE FIGHTING.

12:30.350 --> 12:34.275
TIME FOR...ME TO GO.

12:34.280 --> 12:35.417
>> THEN I GUESS IM DOING

12:35.420 --> 12:39.379
YOU A FAVOR. YOURE WELCOME.

12:39.380 --> 12:42.019
>> DO YOU--

12:42.030 --> 12:44.453
DO YOU THINK DYING HURTS, DOC?

12:44.460 --> 12:48.021
>> FOR YOU? YEAH.

12:48.030 --> 12:50.760
I THINK IT HURTS FOREVER.

13:00.350 --> 13:01.499
>> WHAT THE HELL IS HE DOING

13:01.510 --> 13:02.841
IN MY EXAMINE ROOM?

13:02.850 --> 13:03.839
>> STANDARD PRE-OP.

13:03.850 --> 13:04.839
IF THE SURGERY IS GOING TO BE

13:04.850 --> 13:07.000
HERE AND IM SUCKING 150 POUNDS

13:07.010 --> 13:08.341
OF FAT OUT OF THIS GUY,

13:08.350 --> 13:09.271
THEN I NEED STATE OF THE ART

13:09.280 --> 13:09.883
EQUIPMENT.

13:09.890 --> 13:11.255
>> WERE NOT DOING THIS SURGERY!

13:11.260 --> 13:12.784
>> WERE NOT. I AM.

13:12.790 --> 13:14.781
FOR MY SON.

13:14.790 --> 13:16.485
>> ILL SUE YOU, AND ILL WIN.

13:16.490 --> 13:17.149
>> TRY ME.

13:17.160 --> 13:18.058
>> AND ILL GET A COURT ORDER

13:18.060 --> 13:18.879
TO STOP YOU FROM DOING

13:18.890 --> 13:19.959
THE OPERATION UNTIL

13:19.970 --> 13:23.064
THE CASE IS SETTLED.

13:23.070 --> 13:25.459
[DOOR OPENS, CLOSES]

13:25.470 --> 13:27.290
[CORK POPS]

13:27.300 --> 13:28.927
>> AH. WHOO! COME ON, KIMMY,

13:28.930 --> 13:32.479
HUH? LETS TOAST US.

13:32.480 --> 13:34.471
>> IM NOT DRINKING,

13:34.480 --> 13:35.936
IM PREGNANT.

13:35.940 --> 13:37.407
>> OH, COME ON, A LITTLE

13:37.410 --> 13:39.503
CHAMPAGNE IS NOT GONNA HURT.

13:39.510 --> 13:41.080
JUST A LITTLE BIT.

13:41.090 --> 13:43.342
>> IM NOT DRINKING, CHRISTIAN,

13:43.350 --> 13:45.489
IM PREGNANT.

13:45.490 --> 13:47.446
AND WHAT ARE WE TOASTING,

13:47.450 --> 13:49.896
ANYWAYS? YOU BEING A COMPLETE

13:49.900 --> 13:51.322
ASSHOLE AND NOT CARING ABOUT

13:51.330 --> 13:53.525
ANYBODY BUT YOURSELF?

13:59.000 --> 14:00.365
>> IVE BEEN THINKING LONG

14:00.370 --> 14:03.908
AND HARD ABOUT THE TWO OF US.

14:03.910 --> 14:05.434
[EXHALES]

14:05.440 --> 14:07.908
OH, WE ARE NOT YOUNG ANYMORE,

14:07.910 --> 14:09.969
YOU KNOW? LIKE WE USED TO BE,

14:09.980 --> 14:11.470
LIKE WE WERE WHEN WE FIRST MET.

14:11.480 --> 14:13.345
IVE HAD SEVERAL LIFE LESSONS

14:13.350 --> 14:15.409
SINCE THEN, AND I KNOW YOU HAVE,

14:15.420 --> 14:18.878
TOO. BUT WE ALWAYS KEEP, PHHTT,

14:18.880 --> 14:20.279
YOU KNOW, COMING BACK TO EACH

14:20.290 --> 14:22.520
OTHER. YOU KNOW, NO MATTER WHAT.

14:22.530 --> 14:24.521
IVE NEVER HAD A CONNECTION WITH

14:24.530 --> 14:25.485
SOMEBODY THE WAY THAT I DO WITH

14:25.490 --> 14:26.582
YOU. I KNOW THAT YOU FEEL

14:26.590 --> 14:28.524
THE SAME WAY ABOUT ME.

14:28.530 --> 14:30.088
[SIGHS]

14:30.100 --> 14:32.398
WEVE SEEN THE BEST OF EACH

14:32.400 --> 14:33.992
OTHER AND THE WORST, AND WHEN WE

14:34.000 --> 14:35.262
GET BETWEEN THE SHEETS, ITS--

14:35.270 --> 14:36.862
[CH UCKLES]

14:36.870 --> 14:41.478
ITS MAGIC.

14:41.480 --> 14:44.301
[SIGHS]

14:44.310 --> 14:46.972
I WANT YOU THERE WHEN I GO TO

14:46.980 --> 14:50.052
SLEEP AT NIGHT, AND I WANT YOU

14:50.060 --> 14:53.279
THERE WHEN I WAKE UP IN

14:53.290 --> 14:55.884
THE MORNING.

15:04.270 --> 15:07.364
WILL YOU MARRY ME?

15:07.370 --> 15:09.895
>> WOW, THATS BEAUTIFUL.

15:09.900 --> 15:12.039
>> ITS VINTAGE, BABY.

15:12.040 --> 15:14.508
JUST LIKE US.

15:19.680 --> 15:22.444
ONE SMALL, CAVEAT, SWEETIE PIE.

15:22.450 --> 15:23.940
>> YEAH?

15:23.950 --> 15:26.316
> > NO BABIES.

15:32.260 --> 15:35.093
>> DR. MCNAMARA?

15:35.100 --> 15:37.056
THE, UH, THE VICTIMS FATHERS

15:37.060 --> 15:39.449
HERE.

15:43.510 --> 15:45.432
>> WHEN THEY TOLD ME YOU REFUSED

15:45.440 --> 15:47.067
TO OPERATE ON CLOVIS,

15:47.070 --> 15:49.607
I WAS PRETTY DAMN MAD.

15:49.610 --> 15:52.340
I KNOW I HAD TO MEET YOU FACE TO

15:52.350 --> 15:53.476
FACE SO YOU COULD AT LEAST

15:53.480 --> 15:56.040
HEAR MY SIDE OF THE STORY.

15:56.050 --> 15:57.119
>> WITH ALL DUE RESPECT,

15:57.120 --> 15:58.678
MR. MARTEL, I DONT NEED TO.

15:58.680 --> 16:00.420
I ALREADY KNOW THE DETAILS

16:00.430 --> 16:01.658
OF YOUR DAUGHTERS DEATH,

16:01.660 --> 16:03.025
AND IT DOES NOT CHANGE

16:03.030 --> 16:04.156
MY POSITION AS A DOCTOR.

16:04.160 --> 16:05.559
>> ITS BEEN 15 YEARS SINCE

16:05.560 --> 16:06.686
CLOVIS WAS GIVEN THE DEATH

16:06.690 --> 16:09.682
PENALTY. 15 YEARS. MY DAUGHTER

16:09.690 --> 16:13.296
WAS ONLY 17 WHEN HE KILLED HER.

16:13.300 --> 16:15.689
YOU KNOW, THEY SAY WHEN A FAMILY

16:15.700 --> 16:17.292
MEMBER GETS CANCER, ITS LIKE

16:17.300 --> 16:19.666
THE WHOLE FAMILY GETS CANCER.

16:19.670 --> 16:22.673
IMAGINE WHAT ITS LIKE WHEN

16:22.680 --> 16:25.046
YOUR BABY GIRL IS BRUTALLY

16:25.050 --> 16:26.278
MURDERED.

16:26.280 --> 16:28.100
[KNOCKING ON DOOR]

16:28.110 --> 16:30.089
>> WOULD IT BE ALL RIGHT IF

16:30.090 --> 16:31.580
I USED YOUR PHONE?

16:31.590 --> 16:32.716
>> IM SORRY, WESLEY, BUT ITS

16:32.720 --> 16:33.379
A LITTLE LATE.

16:33.390 --> 16:34.687
>> I JUST WANT TO ORDER A PIZZA.

16:34.690 --> 16:36.749
PLEASE? IM REALLY HUNGRY.

16:36.760 --> 16:38.182
LOOK, PLEASE?

16:38.190 --> 16:39.680
>> WESLEY, I REPORTED YOU TO

16:39.690 --> 16:41.294
POLICE FOR LOOKING IN MY WINDOW.

16:41.300 --> 16:43.598
PLEASE JUST LEAVE ME ALONE.

16:43.600 --> 16:45.522
[SCREAMING]

16:45.530 --> 16:47.293
>> HE TREATED HER LIKE AN

16:47.300 --> 16:49.268
ANIMAL.

16:49.270 --> 16:53.331
>> LOOK, MR. MARTEL, I...

16:53.340 --> 16:54.739
I CANT IMAGINE WHAT

16:54.740 --> 16:56.230
YOUVE BEEN THROUGH.

16:56.240 --> 16:59.334
>> NO, YOU CANT.

16:59.340 --> 17:02.013
MY WIFE DIED OF HEART DISEASE.

17:02.020 --> 17:05.410
THE STRESS OF WAITING, OF NOT

17:05.420 --> 17:08.685
KNOWING IF OR WHEN WE COULD

17:08.690 --> 17:11.750
PUT AN END TO THIS.

17:11.760 --> 17:13.250
[SIGHS]

17:13.260 --> 17:14.693
NOW ITS MY TURN.

17:14.700 --> 17:17.191
CHORDOMA. BASE OF THE SPINE.

17:17.200 --> 17:18.292
>> I KNOW A SURGEON

17:18.300 --> 17:20.359
AT ST. JOSEPHS, UH,

17:20.370 --> 17:21.701
A SPECIALIST

17:21.710 --> 17:23.268
IN BONE CANCER WHOS HAD A LOT

17:23.270 --> 17:24.305
OF SUCCESS WITH GAMMA RAY

17:24.310 --> 17:25.129
AND LASER TECHNOLOGY--

17:25.140 --> 17:26.402
>> NO THANKS, DOC.

17:26.410 --> 17:29.459
I--I--IM HAPPY TO LEAVE.

17:29.470 --> 17:31.779
I JUST DONT WANT TO GO

17:31.780 --> 17:35.079
BEFORE HE DOES.

17:35.080 --> 17:37.219
SO I CAN FACE MY DAUGHTER

17:37.220 --> 17:40.326
AND TELL HER THAT WE PUNISHED

17:40.330 --> 17:43.356
THE MAN WHO TOOK YOUR LIFE.

17:43.360 --> 17:49.287
YOU WERE GIVEN JUSTICE.

17:49.290 --> 17:52.839
JUSTICE, BABY GIRL.

18:03.210 --> 18:04.746
>> HI.

18:04.750 --> 18:06.172
>> HEY. AM I TOO EARLY?

18:06.180 --> 18:07.374
>> NO, NO, IM RUNNING LATE.

18:07.380 --> 18:08.699
COME IN.

18:08.710 --> 18:10.416
>> HEH. GOOD.

18:10.420 --> 18:11.785
>> HOW ARE YOU?

18:11.790 --> 18:13.849
>> GOOD. NICE TO SEE YOU.

18:13.860 --> 18:16.283
OH. OH!

18:16.290 --> 18:17.450
YOU KNOW, I WAS SO SURPRISED

18:17.460 --> 18:18.381
TO GET A CALL.

18:18.390 --> 18:19.482
>> YEAH?

18:19.490 --> 18:20.388
>> YEAH.

18:20.400 --> 18:21.719
>> JUST SURPRISED?

18:21.730 --> 18:23.368
>> WELL, AND HAPPY.

18:23.370 --> 18:24.223
>> MM-HMM.

18:24.230 --> 18:25.094
>> EXCITED.

18:25.100 --> 18:26.260
>> MM. OK, IM GONNA BE RIGHT

18:26.270 --> 18:27.225
BACK, ALL RIGHT?

18:27.230 --> 18:29.391
>> ALL RIGHT.

18:31.180 --> 18:34.377
AH. YOU DID SOME REDECORATING,

18:34.380 --> 18:35.404
HUH?

18:35.410 --> 18:37.207
>> YEAH, I GOT RID OF SOME

18:37.210 --> 18:39.269
STUFF. UH, I READ THIS ARTICLE

18:39.280 --> 18:41.487
SOMEWHERE THAT SAID YOU

18:41.490 --> 18:42.718
SHOULDNT HAVE ANYTHING IN YOUR

18:42.720 --> 18:45.143
HOME IF ITS NOT BEAUTIFUL

18:45.150 --> 18:46.515
OR USEFUL. SO IM JUST TRYING

18:46.520 --> 18:48.715
TO LIVE LIKE THAT.

18:48.720 --> 18:51.257
>> I LIKE IT.

18:51.260 --> 18:52.750
MAKES SENSE.

18:52.760 --> 18:56.218
>> [SIGHS]

19:00.370 --> 19:02.258
>> HEY, YOU KNOW, I WAS THINKING

19:02.270 --> 19:03.407
WE SHOULD CHECK OUT THIS NEW

19:03.410 --> 19:04.468
MEDITERRANEAN RESTAURANT.

19:04.470 --> 19:05.402
A PATIENT OF MINE SAID THAT

19:05.410 --> 19:08.231
ITS SUPPOSED TO BE UNREAL.

19:08.240 --> 19:10.174
>> WELL...

19:10.180 --> 19:11.442
I HOPE YOU CAN CANCEL

19:11.450 --> 19:13.145
THOSE RESERVATIONS.

19:48.850 --> 19:50.886
> > WHAT?

19:50.890 --> 19:52.812
>> HOW FAR ALONG ARE YOU?

19:52.820 --> 19:54.185
> > WHAT?

19:54.190 --> 19:55.452
>> YOUR BREASTS ARE SWOLLEN,

19:55.460 --> 19:56.449
YOUR NIPPLES ARE DARKER

19:56.460 --> 19:57.779
AND YOU HAVE MILD ACNE

19:57.790 --> 19:59.451
FROM THE PROGESTERONE INCREASE.

19:59.460 --> 20:02.327
I GUESS...

20:02.330 --> 20:05.527
7 WEEKS?

20:05.530 --> 20:07.919
>> SIX.

20:07.930 --> 20:09.898
>> WELL...[SIGHS]

20:09.900 --> 20:15.532
WE KNOW ITS NOT MINE, THEN.

20:15.540 --> 20:18.839
AND YET...YOU CALLED ME OVER

20:18.840 --> 20:20.489
HERE TO HAVE SEX WITH YOU

20:20.490 --> 20:22.515
SO YOU COULD, WHAT...

20:22.520 --> 20:25.444
MAKE ME THINK I WAS THE DADDY?

20:25.450 --> 20:27.486
WHY?

20:27.490 --> 20:29.515
>> OH...

20:29.520 --> 20:32.353
[SIGHS]

20:32.360 --> 20:36.922
BECAUSE I CAN BARELY MANAGE ONE.

20:36.930 --> 20:40.536
A SINGLE MOTHER WITH 2 KIDS?

20:40.540 --> 20:43.236
IM NOT GONNA FIND A MAN AGAIN.

20:43.240 --> 20:46.266
AND I CANT DO THIS ON MY OWN,

20:46.270 --> 20:48.807
MIKE.

20:48.810 --> 20:50.846
AND YOU AND I, WE WERE REALLY

20:50.850 --> 20:54.968
GOOD TOGETHER.

20:54.980 --> 20:59.417
>> WE WERE.

20:59.420 --> 21:03.379
>> I AM SO, SO SORRY.

21:03.390 --> 21:05.529
>> YEAH.

21:05.530 --> 21:07.327
ME, TOO.

21:07.330 --> 21:10.868
>> AND I THOUGHT YOUD BE

21:10.870 --> 21:16.797
A REALLY GOOD DAD.

21:16.800 --> 21:19.337
DO YOU THINK YOU COULD POSSIBLY

21:19.340 --> 21:22.548
FORGIVE ME FOR THIS?

21:22.550 --> 21:26.509
>> I HAVE A BETTER IDEA.

21:26.510 --> 21:28.546
MARRY ME.

21:36.060 --> 21:38.449
[HELICOPTERS]

21:38.460 --> 21:39.381
>> DID YOU SEE THAT SWARM

21:39.390 --> 21:41.426
OF NEWS HELICOPTERS?

21:41.430 --> 21:43.068
WHOA!

21:43.070 --> 21:46.767
GLAD YOU CHANGED YOUR MIND.

21:46.770 --> 21:48.795
[THE MERCY SEAT BY NICK CAVE

21:48.800 --> 21:50.062
PLAYING]

21:50.070 --> 21:51.298
>> THE GUNS ARE GONNA HAVE TO

21:51.310 --> 21:52.800
REMAIN OUTSIDE THE O.R.

21:52.810 --> 21:53.799
>> THEWE ALL BEEN SOAKED IN

21:53.810 --> 21:55.630
THE HYDROGEN PEROXIDE GAS-PLASMA

21:55.640 --> 21:57.005
STERILIZER FOR 14 HOURS,

21:57.010 --> 21:59.035
DR. MCNAMARA. THEYRE COMPLETELY

21:59.040 --> 22:00.940
GERM-FREE.

22:00.950 --> 22:01.814
>> WHO ARE YOU?

22:01.820 --> 22:02.787
>> DR. NEAL. IM HERE TO LOOK

22:02.790 --> 22:04.644
OVER DR. CRUZS SHOULDER,

22:04.650 --> 22:05.947
DOUBLE CHECK HER NUMBERS.

22:05.950 --> 22:06.985
>> YEAH, GOD FORBID I MAKE

22:06.990 --> 22:07.945
A MISTAKE AND MR. CLOVIS

22:07.950 --> 22:09.713
NEVER WAKES UP.

22:09.720 --> 22:10.652
>> MY--MY LAWYER SAID THIS IS

22:10.660 --> 22:12.594
COSTING $300,000. THATS A LOT

22:12.600 --> 22:13.726
OF MONEY.

22:13.730 --> 22:15.322
>> EVERYONE LOSES BECAUSE OF

22:15.330 --> 22:16.649
WHAT YOU DID, WESLEY.

22:16.660 --> 22:18.093
>> WHY DONT YOU JUST KILL ME,

22:18.100 --> 22:20.534
THEN, AND JUST GET IT OVER WITH?

22:20.540 --> 22:21.609
>> THATS NOT MY JOB,

22:22.610 --> 22:23.861
>> ALL RIGHT.

22:23.870 --> 22:26.031
COUNT BACK FROM A HUNDRED FOR

22:26.040 --> 22:28.508
ME.

22:28.510 --> 22:30.876
>> 99, 98...

22:30.880 --> 22:32.677
>> AND THE MERCY SEAT

22:32.680 --> 22:34.079
IS WAITING,

22:34.080 --> 22:36.617
AND I THINK MY HEAD IS GLOWING,

22:36.620 --> 22:38.372
AND ANYWAY IM HOPING

22:38.380 --> 22:39.608
TO BE DONE WITH ALL THIS

22:39.620 --> 22:41.724
WEIGHING UP THE TRUTH,

22:41.730 --> 22:43.083
A EYE FOR AN EYE,

22:43.090 --> 22:44.421
A TOOTH FOR A TOOTH,

22:44.430 --> 22:46.079
AND IVE GOT NOTHING LEFT

22:46.090 --> 22:47.626
TO LOSE,

22:47.630 --> 22:49.757
AND IM NOT AFRAID TO DIE,

22:49.760 --> 22:51.398
THE MERCY SEAT IS WAITING

22:51.400 --> 22:54.096
AND I THINK MY HEAD IS BURNING,

22:54.100 --> 22:55.658
AND IN A WAY IM YEARNING

22:55.670 --> 22:57.069
TO BE DONE WITH ALL THIS

22:57.070 --> 22:59.129
MEASURING OF TRUTH,

22:59.140 --> 23:00.539
AN EYE FOR AN EYE

23:00.550 --> 23:01.676
AND A TOOTH FOR A TOOTH,

23:01.680 --> 23:04.706
AND ANYWAY I TOLD THE TRUTH,

23:04.710 --> 23:07.679
AND IM NOT AFRAID TO DIE

23:07.680 --> 23:08.749
>> JESUS, THAT LUNCH WAS

23:08.750 --> 23:09.774
DISGUSTING.

23:09.780 --> 23:10.712
HOW COME YOU AINT FIGHTING

23:10.720 --> 23:12.381
TO SIT ON THE CROWN?

23:12.390 --> 23:13.584
>> CAUSE I DIDNT EAT IT.

23:13.590 --> 23:14.511
>> MCNAMARA, GRAB YOUR SHIT,

23:14.520 --> 23:15.589
YOURE GETTING TRANSFERRED.

23:15.590 --> 23:17.615
>> AND THE MERCY SEAT IS

23:17.620 --> 23:18.689
BURNING,

23:18.690 --> 23:21.124
AND I THINK MY HEAD IS GLOWIN,

23:21.130 --> 23:23.519
AND ANYWAY IM HOPING TO BE DONE

23:23.530 --> 23:25.589
WITH ALL THIS WEIGHING

23:25.600 --> 23:26.726
OUT THE TRUTH,

23:26.730 --> 23:27.662
AN EYE FOR AN EYE

23:27.670 --> 23:29.126
AND A TOOTH FOR A TOOTH

23:29.130 --> 23:30.062
>> I DONT LIKE RELEASING

23:30.070 --> 23:31.139
INMATES BEFORE TH EYRE

23:31.140 --> 23:32.676
REHABILITATED.

23:32.680 --> 23:33.669
>> IM GETTING OUT OF HERE?

23:33.680 --> 23:34.601
>> I KNOW ILL SEE YOU

23:34.610 --> 23:35.599
IN HERE AGAIN.

23:35.610 --> 23:36.599
>> THE MERCY SEAT IS WAITING,

23:36.610 --> 23:38.828
AND I THINK MY HEAD IS BURNING,

23:38.840 --> 23:40.683
THE WAY IM YEARNING

23:40.690 --> 23:41.679
TO BE DONE--

23:41.690 --> 23:42.884
>> NO, NO, NO,

23:42.890 --> 23:44.710
THERES NO NEED FOR THAT.

23:44.720 --> 23:45.880
>> AN EYE FOR AN EYE

23:45.890 --> 23:46.879
AND A TOOTH FOR A TOOTH,

23:46.890 --> 23:49.541
AND ANYWAY I TOLD THE TRUTH,

23:49.550 --> 23:53.623
AND IM AFRAID I TOLD A LIE

23:59.630 --> 24:01.905
>> AND WHOS GOING TO BE DRIVING

24:01.910 --> 24:03.161
YOU HOME TODAY?

24:03.170 --> 24:04.159
>> ME.

24:04.170 --> 24:05.603
>> WE CANT LET YOU RISK DRIVING

24:05.610 --> 24:06.702
AFTER THE PROCEDURE.

24:06.710 --> 24:08.109
>> OK, WELL, I DONT REALLY HAVE

24:08.110 --> 24:10.431
ANYONE THAT I CAN CALL, SO...

24:10.440 --> 24:11.509
>> IM SURE YOU KNOW SOMEONE

24:11.520 --> 24:12.214
WHO COULD TAKE OFF

24:12.220 --> 24:14.711
AN HOUR AND A HALF.

